window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>In best-selling author Katie MacAlister’s <i>Love in the Time of Dragons</i>, suburban mom Tully Sullivan wakes up in a far-off place surrounded by strangers—many of them muscular, sexy ones—claiming to be dragons. They insist Tully is a dragon, too, and that she’s committed crimes deserving of death. Now Tully must disprove the allegations before time runs out.</p>"; 
